$BR
\( 10 % \)  concentration solution in  \{ans_rule(10) \} liters $BR
\( 20 % \) concentration solution in  \{ans_rule(10) \} liters $BR
\( 50 % \) concentration solution in  \{ans_rule(10) \} liters $BR


c) Use 2 liters of the \( 50 % \) solution.
$BR
\( 10 % \) concentration solution in  \{ans_rule(10) \} liters $BR
\( 20 % \) concentration solution in  \{ans_rule(10) \} liters $BR
\( 50 % \) concentration solution in  \{ans_rule(10) \} liters $BR
